{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC13_ODI_100.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x23,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "I wonder what happened to Ms. Odelia since last time... I wonder if she's fixed..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Welcome to the Zweiteturm.<CR>Would you like a tour?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Ms. Odelia! I'm so glad you're fixed!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x197,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I apologize for all the trouble I caused. I am completely back to normal."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, it is thanks to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I didn't do anything. Mr. Keith is the one who fixed you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Well, it was an easy task for someone like me. I thought it might be tricky to restore her memory, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Even when her temperature was high, she was able to maintain the circuit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Thanks to that, the rest was easy. It was fortunate that she didn't lose her memory."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I'm glad. What would have happened if she lost her memory...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "She would've forgotten everything, of course. Even about you and me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe6,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "And if an automaton loses its memory, it'll never return."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see... Mr. Keith, thank you very much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe8,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Why are you thanking me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Because you protected Ms. Odelia's important memories..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Either way, it's amazing that you were able to fix Ms. Odelia..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x161,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I didn't even have a clue about what to do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "That was also an application of alchemy. You'll eventually be able to do it yourself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I-I wonder if that's true...<CR>It's like being a doctor..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "However, she was made during the height of alchemical prosperity, so she has a very sophisticated structure."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "It was a great opportunity,<CR>so I made sure to perform a<CR>thorough investigation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x116,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "...You have seen everything of me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Seen, everything...?<CR>Wh-Wh-What does that mean...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I think it is necessary to clearly define where your responsibilities lie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "What responsibilities...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Well. How about becoming my new master?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I decline. I have no desire to be tied down to something."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x117,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "I do not think this is a bad condition..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x119,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "All of my abilities and functions will become yours."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I'm fine. I'm satisfied with just being able to read the books here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Keith, shouldn't you be<CR>taking responsibility,<CR>like Ms. Odelia said...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "See? Even Ayesha is saying this, so you should become my new master..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "I don't care! I can't deal with this!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xad,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Oh, please wait, Master!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "(Mr. Keith ran away... I think this is a wonderful thing...)"
        }
    ]
}